Regulation (EC) No 3282/94 is hereby amended as follows:
1.  Article 6 (2) shall be replaced by the following text:
'2.  The benefit of preferences shall not be granted to products of Annex I or II of Regulation  (EEC) No 3833/90 falling within CN codes 0409  00 and 2401 and Chapters 6, 7, 8 and 20 originating  in South Africa, with the exception of the products appearing in Annex I to this Regulation.`;
2.  Article 8 shall be replaced by the following text:
'Article 8 The technical amendments to the Annexes to Regulations (EEC) No 3833/90, (EEC) No 3835/90 and (EEC)  No 3900/91 appear in Annex II to this Regulation.`;
3.  the existing Annex shall become Annex II and Annex I set out in the Annex to this Regulation  shall be inserted.
